{
  "stem": "20575.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a lot of people came to visit us and they tried to make it as normal-- as normal as possible.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And wait, what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it turned out-- which was very lucky for me-- don't forget, there were a lot of educated people there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This one was a professor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- a German professor-- Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Kornitzer, with his wife.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there another one was a math-- math professor, with his wife.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Forgot his name.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But somehow, while I was there and I couldn't go to school, I always ask him to give me something to-- to-- to learn.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and I took a little math from him and a little German from them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were discussing things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, Professor Kornitzer was a great help to us when I came back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Don't forget, I was already 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had no formal schooling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he vouched for me so that I could make-- could go on and go for higher education.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he said, she will-- she'll be able to catch up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I got-- you know, I got into a class so I could go on with my education after the war, because of the-- Professor Kornitzer.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is the-- at-- that-- I got-- first, from-- when we got thrown out from the school, there was a school, it's called [NON-ENGLISH] in a second district, which was later a gathering camp for the-- for us to send us away.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But before, it was a school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all the Jewish children from all over Vienna had to go to this school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But also, not for long, because that also was converted into a camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
